#: ../../../interop/dbus.rst:51
msgid ""
"dbus-daemon can enforce various policies based on the UID/GID of the "
"processes that are connected to it. It is thus a good idea to run helpers as "
"different UID from QEMU and set appropriate policies."
msgstr ""

